Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory641.jpg'}
{1: 'DialogEnable'}
{3: 'After a hectic afternoon, you finally get a few minutes to relax, leaning back on the break room couch.'}
{3: "You pop open the cherry soda on the tea table, and the fizz washes away the morning's tiredness."}
{3: "The artificial cherry flavor is spot-on, sweet with a tiny bit of tart, you can't help but chug it."}
{3: 'You sink into the soft cushions, letting yourself drift off into a midday nap...'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{1: 'DialogEnable'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory538.png'}
{2: '??', 3: 'The backend team\'s going nuts, and you, the "culprit", are just chilling here?'}
{1: 'DialogDisable'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryZhengyanNew01.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryZhengyanNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory641.jpg'}
{1: '1', 3: "A cool, soft touch wakes you up. You open your eyes and see Teddy's finger on your forehead."}
{3: 'Her face is as calm as always, not showing a thing, but she smells strongly of freshly baked food.'}
{3: 'Plus, she really leans into the word "culprit", and, oddly, explains everything in detail, which she never does. Putting it all together, you know she is faking it.'}
{2: 'The... culprit?', 3: '26', 4: 'What are you talking about?', 5: '26'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Didn't you hear? You fell asleep for five minutes, forgot to send the mission data, and now Babylonia's firewall is down.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Those guys are freaking out, looking everywhere for you.', 4: '1'}
{2: "That's impossible...", 3: '30'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Look, no point in making excuses. The damage is done.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Your only shot at avoiding those angry programmers is to hide out with me here in the break room.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "You're stuck here for the rest of the afternoon.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{3: 'Teddy holds out her wrist, and the word "ALERT" scrolls big on the screen from her watch terminal.'}
{3: 'She tilts her head, giving you a serious look, like, "See? I\'m not kidding."'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab'}
{2: "Something's still not right...", 3: '42'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: "What's bothering you?", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm not in your line of work, and I definitely don't know the tech stuff like you do...", 3: '45'}
{2: 'But the Teddy I know is way too good to let something like this slip.', 3: '46'}
{3: 'As soon as she finishes, a sly smile spreads across her face.'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Been a few days, and you've turned into a real charmer, huh?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "Never mind. I knew you wouldn't buy my story anyway.", 4: '1'}
{3: "She relaxes a bit, then tosses her tablet-sized mini-terminal, which she's been hiding, to the Commandant across from her."}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "If you're so keen on the truth, then take a look.", 4: '1'}
{2: '(Take the terminal)'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{3: 'You enter the terminal password, go to the mission notifications, and scroll down to your "Latest Notification".'}
{3: 'Then you spot a bright red line: "EMERGENCY MISSION".'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunNew.prefab'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Man, you have some terrible luck, huh?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Last time it was the team lottery, and this time, on your birthday, everyone has to do an emergency mission report.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'I went to the store early for baking powder and frosting, and even asked my annoying brother for help, just to get fresh cherries from the conservation area...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'But because of you, all my plans are ruined. So, how are you going to make it up to me?', 4: '1'}
{3: "That's why she smelled like baked food, not her usual scent."}
{2: "I'm sorry. Next time, I'll definitely...", 3: '76'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: '"Next time" is the last thing I want to hear.', 4: '1'}
{3: "You don't get to finish your sentence, because Teddy moves suddenly."}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'If I want something, I get it, plain and simple.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "【kuroname】, haven't you heard? Expired canned cherries never taste the same.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Teddy moves closer with a sneaky grin and snatches the flashing terminal from your hand.'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Sorry, that last part was a fib.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'Actually, I went ahead and submitted that mission for you while you were sleeping.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "But watching you drink all my cherry drinks without asking, then sleep like a log, not even noticing my surprise... it's hard not to be mad...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: "So, a little teasing isn't too bad, is it?", 4: '1'}
{3: "Her smile, like her sweet scent, feels dangerous, but you can't look away."}
{2: 'Teddy', 3: 'So, what are you going to do to make it up to me today?', 4: '1'}
